{
  "video_id": "sz77x05rySc",
  "title": "Ian Ritchie: The day I turned down Tim Berners-Lee",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 15260.0,
      "end_time": 17259.0,
      "text": "Well we all know the World Wide Web"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17260.0,
      "end_time": 21260.0,
      "text": "has absolutely transformed publishing, broadcasting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 21260.0,
      "end_time": 23260.0,
      "text": "commerce and social connectivity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 23260.0,
      "end_time": 25260.0,
      "text": "but where did it all come from?"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 25260.0,
      "end_time": 27260.0,
      "text": "And I&#39;ll quote three people:"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27260.0,
      "end_time": 30260.0,
      "text": "Vannevar Bush, Doug Engelbart and Tim Berners-Lee."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 30260.0,
      "end_time": 32260.0,
      "text": "So let&#39;s just run through these guys."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 32259.0,
      "end_time": 34260.0,
      "text": "This is Vannevar Bush."
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 34260.0,
      "end_time": 37260.0,
      "text": "Vannevar Bush was the U.S. government&#39;s chief scientific adviser during the war."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37260.0,
      "end_time": 39260.0,
      "text": "And in 1945,"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 39260.0,
      "end_time": 42260.0,
      "text": "he published an article in a magazine called Atlantic Monthly."
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42260.0,
      "end_time": 45260.0,
      "text": "And the article was called \"As We May Think.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45260.0,
      "end_time": 47260.0,
      "text": "And what Vannevar Bush was saying"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 47260.0,
      "end_time": 50260.0,
      "text": "was the way we use information is broken."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 50260.0,
      "end_time": 53260.0,
      "text": "We don&#39;t work in terms of libraries"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 53260.0,
      "end_time": 55260.0,
      "text": "and catalog systems and so forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55260.0,
      "end_time": 57260.0,
      "text": "The brain works by association."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 57260.0,
      "end_time": 60260.0,
      "text": "With one item in its thought, it snaps instantly to the next item."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 60260.0,
      "end_time": 62260.0,
      "text": "And the way information is structured"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 62260.0,
      "end_time": 65259.0,
      "text": "is totally incapable of keeping up with this process."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 65260.00000000001,
      "end_time": 67260.0,
      "text": "And so he suggested a machine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 67260.0,
      "end_time": 69260.0,
      "text": "and he called it the memex."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 69260.0,
      "end_time": 71260.0,
      "text": "And the memex would link information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 71260.0,
      "end_time": 74260.0,
      "text": "one piece of information to a related piece of information and so forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 74260.0,
      "end_time": 76260.0,
      "text": "Now this was in 1945."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 76260.0,
      "end_time": 78260.0,
      "text": "A computer in those days"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 78260.0,
      "end_time": 81260.0,
      "text": "was something the secret services used to use for code breaking."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 81260.0,
      "end_time": 83260.0,
      "text": "And nobody knew anything about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 83260.0,
      "end_time": 85260.0,
      "text": "So this was before the computer was invented."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 85260.0,
      "end_time": 87260.0,
      "text": "And he proposed this machine called the memex."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 87260.0,
      "end_time": 90260.0,
      "text": "And he had a platform where you linked information to other information,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 90260.0,
      "end_time": 92260.0,
      "text": "and then you could call it up at will."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 92260.0,
      "end_time": 94260.0,
      "text": "So spinning forward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 94260.0,
      "end_time": 96260.0,
      "text": "one of the guys who read this article was a guy called Doug Engelbart,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 96260.0,
      "end_time": 98260.0,
      "text": "and he was a U.S. Air Force officer."
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 98260.0,
      "end_time": 101260.0,
      "text": "And he was reading it in their library in the Far East."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 101260.0,
      "end_time": 103260.0,
      "text": "And he was so inspired by this article,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 103260.0,
      "end_time": 105260.0,
      "text": "it kind of directed the rest of his life."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 105260.0,
      "end_time": 108260.0,
      "text": "And by the mid-60s, he was able to put this into action"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 108260.0,
      "end_time": 111260.0,
      "text": "when he worked at the Stanford Research Lab in California."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 112260.0,
      "end_time": 114260.0,
      "text": "He built a system."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 114260.0,
      "end_time": 117260.0,
      "text": "The system was designed to augment human intelligence, it was called."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 117260.0,
      "end_time": 120260.0,
      "text": "And in a premonition of today&#39;s world"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 120260.0,
      "end_time": 122260.0,
      "text": "of cloud computing and softwares of service,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 122260.0,
      "end_time": 124260.0,
      "text": "his system was called NLS"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 124260.0,
      "end_time": 126260.0,
      "text": "for oN-Line System."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 126260.0,
      "end_time": 128259.0,
      "text": "And this is Doug Engelbart."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 128258.99999999999,
      "end_time": 131260.0,
      "text": "He was giving a presentation at the Fall Joint Computer Conference"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 131260.0,
      "end_time": 134260.0,
      "text": "in 1968."
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 134260.0,
      "end_time": 136260.0,
      "text": "What he showed --"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 136260.0,
      "end_time": 139260.0,
      "text": "he sat on a stage like this, and he demonstrated this system."
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 139260.0,
      "end_time": 141260.0,
      "text": "He had his head mic like I&#39;ve got."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 141260.0,
      "end_time": 143260.0,
      "text": "And he works this system."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 143260.0,
      "end_time": 145260.0,
      "text": "And you can see, he&#39;s working between documents"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 145260.0,
      "end_time": 147260.0,
      "text": "and graphics and so forth."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 147260.0,
      "end_time": 149260.0,
      "text": "And he&#39;s driving it all"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 149260.0,
      "end_time": 151260.0,
      "text": "with this platform here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 151260.0,
      "end_time": 153260.0,
      "text": "with a five-finger keyboard"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 153260.0,
      "end_time": 155260.0,
      "text": "and the world&#39;s first computer mouse,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 155260.0,
      "end_time": 157260.0,
      "text": "which he specially designed in order to do this system."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 157260.0,
      "end_time": 159260.0,
      "text": "So this is where the mouse came from as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 159260.0,
      "end_time": 161260.0,
      "text": "So this is Doug Engelbart."
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 161260.0,
      "end_time": 163260.0,
      "text": "The trouble with Doug Engelbart&#39;s system"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 163260.0,
      "end_time": 166260.0,
      "text": "was that the computers in those days cost several million pounds."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 166260.0,
      "end_time": 168260.0,
      "text": "So for a personal computer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 168260.0,
      "end_time": 170260.0,
      "text": "a few million pounds was like having a personal jet plane;"
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 170260.0,
      "end_time": 172260.0,
      "text": "it wasn&#39;t really very practical."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 172260.0,
      "end_time": 174260.0,
      "text": "But spin on to the 80s"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 174260.0,
      "end_time": 176260.0,
      "text": "when personal computers did arrive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 176260.0,
      "end_time": 178260.0,
      "text": "then there was room for this kind of system on personal computers."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 178260.0,
      "end_time": 180260.0,
      "text": "And my company, OWL"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 180260.0,
      "end_time": 183260.0,
      "text": "built a system called Guide for the Apple Macintosh."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 183260.0,
      "end_time": 187260.0,
      "text": "And we delivered the world&#39;s first hypertext system."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 187260.0,
      "end_time": 189260.0,
      "text": "And this began to get a head of steam."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 189260.0,
      "end_time": 191260.0,
      "text": "Apple introduced a thing called HyperCard,"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 191260.0,
      "end_time": 193260.0,
      "text": "and they made a bit of a fuss about it."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 193260.0,
      "end_time": 196260.0,
      "text": "They had a 12-page supplement in the Wall Street Journal the day it launched."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 196260.0,
      "end_time": 198260.0,
      "text": "The magazines started to cover it."
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 198260.0,
      "end_time": 200260.0,
      "text": "Byte magazine and Communications at the ACM"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 200260.0,
      "end_time": 202260.0,
      "text": "had special issues covering hypertext."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 202260.0,
      "end_time": 204260.0,
      "text": "We developed a PC version of this product"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 204260.0,
      "end_time": 206260.0,
      "text": "as well as the Macintosh version."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 206260.0,
      "end_time": 209260.0,
      "text": "And our PC version became quite mature."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 209260.0,
      "end_time": 212260.0,
      "text": "These are some examples of this system in action in the late 80s."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 213260.0,
      "end_time": 216260.0,
      "text": "You were able to deliver documents, were able to do it over networks."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 216260.0,
      "end_time": 218260.0,
      "text": "We developed a system such"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 218260.0,
      "end_time": 220260.0,
      "text": "that it had a markup language based on html."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 220260.0,
      "end_time": 223260.0,
      "text": "We called it hml: hypertext markup language."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 223260.0,
      "end_time": 225260.0,
      "text": "And the system was capable of doing"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 225260.0,
      "end_time": 229260.0,
      "text": "very, very large documentation systems over computer networks."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 229260.0,
      "end_time": 232260.0,
      "text": "So I took this system to a trade show in Versailles near Paris"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 232260.0,
      "end_time": 235260.0,
      "text": "in late November 1990."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 235260.0,
      "end_time": 237260.0,
      "text": "And I was approached by a nice young man called Tim Berners-Lee"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 237260.0,
      "end_time": 239260.0,
      "text": "who said, \"Are you Ian Ritchie?\" and I said, \"Yeah.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 239260.0,
      "end_time": 241260.0,
      "text": "And he said, \"I need to talk to you.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 241260.0,
      "end_time": 244260.0,
      "text": "And he told me about his proposed system called the World Wide Web."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 244260.0,
      "end_time": 247260.0,
      "text": "And I thought, well, that&#39;s got a pretentious name,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 247260.0,
      "end_time": 250260.0,
      "text": "especially since the whole system ran on his computer in his office."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 250260.0,
      "end_time": 253260.0,
      "text": "But he was completely convinced that his World Wide Web"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 253260.0,
      "end_time": 255260.0,
      "text": "would take over the world one day."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 255260.0,
      "end_time": 257260.0,
      "text": "And he tried to persuade me to write the browser for it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 257260.0,
      "end_time": 260260.0,
      "text": "because his system didn&#39;t have any graphics or fonts or layout or anything;"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 260260.0,
      "end_time": 262260.0,
      "text": "it was just plain text."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 262260.0,
      "end_time": 265260.0,
      "text": "I thought, well, you know, interesting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 265260.0,
      "end_time": 267260.0,
      "text": "but a guy from CERN, he&#39;s not going to do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 267260.0,
      "end_time": 269260.0,
      "text": "So we didn&#39;t do it."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 269260.0,
      "end_time": 271260.0,
      "text": "In the next couple of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 271260.0,
      "end_time": 273260.0,
      "text": "the hypertext community didn&#39;t recognize him either."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 273260.0,
      "end_time": 276260.0,
      "text": "In 1992, his paper was rejected for the Hypertext Conference."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 276260.0,
      "end_time": 279260.0,
      "text": "In 1993,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 279260.0,
      "end_time": 281260.0,
      "text": "there was a table at the conference in Seattle,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 281260.0,
      "end_time": 283260.0,
      "text": "and a guy called Marc Andreessen"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 283260.0,
      "end_time": 286260.0,
      "text": "was demonstrating his little browser for the World Wide Web."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 286260.0,
      "end_time": 288260.0,
      "text": "And I saw it, and I thought, yep, that&#39;s it."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 288260.0,
      "end_time": 291260.0,
      "text": "And the very next year, in 1994, we had the conference here in Edinburgh,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 291260.0,
      "end_time": 295260.0,
      "text": "and I had no opposition in having Tim Berners-Lee as the keynote speaker."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 295260.0,
      "end_time": 297260.0,
      "text": "So that puts me in pretty illustrious company."
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 297260.0,
      "end_time": 299260.0,
      "text": "There was a guy called Dick Rowe"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 299260.0,
      "end_time": 301260.0,
      "text": "who was at Decca Records and turned down The Beatles."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 301260.0,
      "end_time": 303260.0,
      "text": "There was a guy called Gary Kildall"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 303260.0,
      "end_time": 305260.0,
      "text": "who went flying his plane"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 305260.0,
      "end_time": 307260.0,
      "text": "when IBM came looking for an operating system"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 307260.0,
      "end_time": 309260.0,
      "text": "for the IBM PC,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 309260.0,
      "end_time": 311260.0,
      "text": "and he wasn&#39;t there, so they went back to see Bill Gates."
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 311260.0,
      "end_time": 313260.0,
      "text": "And the 12 publishers"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 313260.0,
      "end_time": 316260.0,
      "text": "who turned down J.K. Rowling&#39;s Harry Potter, I guess."
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 316260.0,
      "end_time": 318260.0,
      "text": "On the other hand, there&#39;s Marc Andreessen"
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 318260.0,
      "end_time": 320260.0,
      "text": "who wrote the world&#39;s first browser for the World Wide Web."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 320260.0,
      "end_time": 322260.0,
      "text": "And according to Fortune magazine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 322260.0,
      "end_time": 324260.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s worth 700 million dollars."
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 324260.0,
      "end_time": 326260.0,
      "text": "But is he happy?"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 326260.0,
      "end_time": 328260.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 328260.0,
      "end_time": 335260.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}